OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: One mother's
OL,4,Cfight for road trauma support
OL,6,FFor many of my guests, tragedy marks a
OL,7,Fturning point in their lives.
OL,8,FSometimes it inspires them to fight
OL,9,Ffor a cause, other times it can break
OL,10,Fa person but either way, life is never
OL,11,Fthe same.
OL,13,FFor Monica Heaney, after losing her 27
OL,14,Fyear old son Karl in a car accident on
OL,15,Fthe A1 in 2018, her life and those of
OL,16,Fher family members, changed in a split
OL,17,Fsecond. Yet through her own trauma,
OL,18,Fwith a genuine generosity of spirit,
OL,19,Fshe recognised the ripple effect of
OL,20,Fwhat had happened.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
