PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784119706
OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: One mother's
OL,4,Cfight for road trauma support
OL,6,F'There was a man who came to Karl's
OL,7,Fwake. He had witnessed what had
OL,8,Fhappened...and I kept thinking about
OL,9,Fhim and thinking about who did he have
OL,10,Fto talk to?'
OL,12,FIt wasn't the first time Monica had
OL,13,Ffaced life-changing trauma. Some years
OL,14,Fpreviously she had developed breast
OL,15,Fcancer but she said in terms of
OL,16,Fsupport, it was a different experience.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784119706
OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: One mother's
OL,4,Cfight for road trauma support
OL,6,F'The nurse had details of multiple
OL,7,Fcharities. I didn't have to think of
OL,8,Fthe best wig to wear. I didn't have to
OL,9,Fthink of financial hardship. I was
OL,10,Fcarried and I assumed it would be the
OL,11,Fsame this time.'
OL,13,FBut as Monica sought for the help for
OL,14,Fher and the family to get them through
OL,15,Fthe loss of Karl, she realised it
OL,16,Fsimply didn't exist. There was a
OL,17,Flimited amount of support for parents
OL,18,Fwho had lost a child on the roads but
OL,19,Ffor the extended family, Karl's
OL,20,Ffriends, witnesses...there was nothing.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784119706
OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: One mother's
OL,4,Cfight for road trauma support
OL,6,FAnd so The Road Ahead NI was born.
OL,7,FIt's goal is to provide people-centric
OL,8,Fsupport to anyone who has been
OL,9,Faffected by a road traffic collision,
OL,10,Fincluding those who have caused
OL,11,Faccidents. Monica understands the
OL,12,Ftrauma that has been caused by Karl's
OL,13,Faccident and believes that support
OL,14,Fprovided by people who have been
OL,15,Fthrough this life-changing event can
OL,16,Fbetter support those who come to the
OL,17,Fcharity looking for help.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
