FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1784119706
OL,3,CGoing the Extra Mile: One mother's
OL,4,Cfight for road trauma support
OL,6,FAs the number of road collisions
OL,7,Fincreases and as more people are dying
OL,8,Fon our roads, more people are looking
OL,9,Ffor help. For Monica, it shows there
OL,10,Fis a space for these services. It's an
OL,11,Fissue which affects thousands of
OL,12,Fpeople across NI and for her, this is
OL,13,FKarl's legacy. She does this work in
OL,14,Fhis name.
OL,16,F'No one should travel this journey
OL,17,Falone'
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
